{"tid":2037451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白警爆料 有狗扮記者扮手足幫推上熱門","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T17:42:37.000Z","uid":125168,"like":392,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":169,"replies":[{"pid":"f86756c36899997c57663a96d30792de5d49e4a2","tid":2037451,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"幫手散出去 白警爆料<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬警司John Corroll 同幾個鬼佬差人 而家喺中環金鐘一帶扮外國記者四圍搵啲小朋友傾計, 大家提高警覺<br />\n<br />\n另外元朗十八鄉鄉黑有3車黑衣人扮黑暴而家係北角差館等緊指示, 應該會係稍後時間會去扮手足搞事<br />\n<br />\n大家請提高警覺性<br />\n<br />\n#讀者報料 #自行判斷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/polyufast/14262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpolyufast%2F14262&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=c4bda902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/polyufast/14262</a>"},{"pid":"3321fec87924f225fd42c7fb3916a22281c1165c","tid":2037451,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309f8e920d65fc9389f6b753147f50c6e9cf16c5","tid":2037451,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c705c42bdc6bb9fb408bb3eed47acd521e18d5e","tid":2037451,"uid":141668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bf8f339be21d74206f664b13955eebd9111802","tid":2037451,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdca1306eecaa3a3395d9244c65d0a84a7c4d11","tid":2037451,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:52:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df3c06e1ea784856e8a69ae09a56e5cafa9202c9","tid":2037451,"uid